raw_text = "~ start
#6pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Mabel: It's doneeee 😮‍💨
Mabel: I think it went okay? I was a shaky mess though
Mabel: I'm so exhausted, I need my sleep!!
Mabel: Just packing up to head home now
do Story.set_location(\"college_square_gardens\")
Player: Yeah your class finished late today huh
Mabel: Oh really?
Mabel: OMG YOU'RE RIGHT!!
Mabel: I was picked last to present today
do Story.set_location(\"main_street\")
Mabel: It's already pitch black outside 🥺
Mabel: Why does it get dark so early ughh
Mabel: You know how I feel about the dark babe 😣
Player: Text me the whole way home then?
Mabel: Is that okay? My hero 🥺
Mabel: I'll take the shortcut through town
Mabel: Okay venturing out now, wish me luck against the boogeyman 🫡
Mabel: sfx: highmoan3: Eep!!
Mabel: Thought: Who did I just bump into??
do echo_set([\"187\"])
do heart(1)
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh! S-sorry!!
Mabel: Thought: ...wait
Mabel: Thought: It's him. That guy from my Social
Mabel: Thought: I forgot about that!! Did he wait that long?
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh, um, hi again
Mabel: sfx: none: Haha yeah, just got out of class
Mabel: Thought: How did he even know I'm here??
Mabel: One sec babe
Player: Everything okay?
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Thought: Uhm... how do I even bring this up to babe?
Mabel: Thought: I'll just ditch him by walking a little fast!
Mabel: Thought: You got this Mabes!
Mabel: Everything is totes okay! Just getting started on my way home!
Mabel: sfx: none: Walk me home? Oh, you really don't have to...
Mabel: Thought: It's so dark though. And I HATE walking alone
Mabel: Thought: And he's being kind of nice about it
Mabel: Thought: I won't be bad by just taking advantage here right?
Mabel: sfx: none: O-okay, sure. Thank you, that's really nice of you
Player: You went quiet, everything ok?
Mabel: Yeah!! Sorry, all good 😅
Mabel: Trying to focus on walking home hehe
Mabel: You know me, just zooming! 🤪
Mabel: Thought: \"Hey babe, yeah just walking home with this random guy I just met\"
Mabel: Thought: DOES NOT SOUND OKAY!!
Mabel: Thought: It's a nothing burger, totally nothing. One time thing.
Player: Okay sounds good 😅
Mabel: Aye aye, everything is good 🫡
Mabel: sfx: none: Huh? Am I single?
Mabel: Thought: If I tell him no, is he just gonna leave me here all by myself?
Mabel: Thought: In the middle of the dark??
Mabel: Thought: Think Mabel!
Mabel: Thought: I don't want him to just walk away here
Mabel: PinkThought: He's a bit muscular... I feel a little bit safer with him around
Mabel: sfx: none: Uhm.. yeah haha, totally single hehe
Mabel: PinkThought: That little giggle surely worked like a charm!
Mabel: Just reaching half way babe!
Player: Good! Keep me updated
Mabel: Seriously, I got this!! No sweat
Mabel: sfx: highmoan1: EEK!!
do Story.mabel_groped(\"RawDawg\")
do heart(2)
do echo_set([\"188\"])
Mabel: sfx: none: Uhm...
Mabel: sfx: none: No nothing, nevermind
Mabel: sfx: none: It's, um, just up this way
Mabel: Thought: His hand is..
Mabel: Thought: It's on my butt!?
Mabel: Thought: Why is his hand on my butt...??
Mabel: Thought: Is it some kind of mistake?
Mabel: Thought: Do I say something?? Do I move away?
Mabel: Thought: Is this uhmm.. normal?
Mabel: Thought: What if it's an accident and I make it all awkward?
Mabel: Thought: UGH idk what to do, I'm way too exhausted to think about this
Mabel: sfx: none: Haha uhm.. y-yeah, right up here!
do Story.set_location(\"college_grounds\")
Mabel: I'm like 2 steps away from home babe!!
Player: That's good! Got home pretty fast
Mabel: PinkThought: I feel like his hand is bigger than babe's
Mabel: Hold on one sec
Mabel: sfx: none: Your room?
Mabel: sfx: none: Uhm.. isn't it a bit late for coffee?
Mabel: sfx: none: Huh? Like what..?
Mabel: sfx: none: Netflix? Ah.. I mean I'm just a little tired right now but thanks
Mabel: sfx: none: I had a big presentation
Mabel: Thought: \"Hot\"? Did he just call me that?
Mabel: sfx: none: Hot for a nerd? Haha, I dunno.. maybe
Mabel: PinkThought: When was the last time babe called me that...?
Mabel: Thought: Oh we're here already?
Mabel: Thought: That felt even faster than walking alone
Mabel: Thought: Was it because I was so nervous? Or... was it because..
Mabel: sfx: none: T-Thank you...
Mabel: sfx: none: Uhm again some time?... maybe sure...
do advance_time(0, 5)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do heart(0)
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Thought: Phew, it felt like he wanted to invite me somewhere
Mabel: Thought: But what did he mean by \"keep trying\"? Is he seriously going to follow me around
Mabel: Thought: That was WAY too scary and I don't want to worry babe 
Mabel: Made it home safe!! Easy 😌
Player: See? Not so hard huh!
Mabel: Hehe... yup. Safe and sound
Mabel: All because I had you on with me 🥰
Player: Anytime 🥰
Mabel: Thought: I just have to avoid that guy from now on
Mabel: PinkThought: My butt feels a little weird
Mabel: PinkThought: But in a good way...
Mabel: Thought: Why am I still thinking about that!?
Mabel: Thought: There's no noise right now, it's probably too early... Maybe I can sneak in some sleep
Mabel: I'm gonna pass out babe
Mabel: I'd ask you how your day was but...
Mabel: But I'm seriously super exhausted
Mabel: img: mabel/190
Mabel: 😴😪
Player: Night Mabes
Mabel: Lv u
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
